Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.25,0:22:27.20,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you are my only shooting star
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.39,0:22:29.19,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢動いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.42,0:22:34.61,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人の鼓動触れた時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:41.48,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねぇ　今誰を思っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.83,0:22:49.22,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硝子星に眺めた切ないその横顔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.48,0:22:55.46,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微かな距離でも届かなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.70,0:23:00.06,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言い訳ばっかりを束ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:03.02,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今を逃げてた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:06.41,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱虫だったあの頃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.66,0:23:14.41,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩れそうな弱さと向き合える気がしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:18.14,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出すよ 明日の扉開けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.39,0:23:21.81,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君が居る場所まで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.05,0:23:28.99,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃し続けてきた思い伝えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.19,0:23:36.28,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,here in my house君が笑う 何気ない世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:45.46,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞こえるその声が 私の涙強くする
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.49,0:23:49.21,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you are my only shooting star
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.25,0:22:27.20,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是划过我生命唯一的流星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.39,0:22:29.19,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想开始悸动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.42,0:22:34.61,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们触碰到彼此的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:41.48,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你正在想念谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.83,0:22:49.22,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透过玻璃星星看到你的侧脸 让人如此无法割舍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.48,0:22:55.46,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使近在咫尺 却也无法向你传达
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.70,0:23:00.06,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出种种借口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:03.02,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避着现实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:06.41,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的我如此胆小
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.66,0:23:14.41,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在终于鼓起勇气直面那溃不成军的软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:18.14,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发吧 打开通向明天的门扉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.39,0:23:21.81,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往你所在的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.05,0:23:28.99,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想向你倾诉那份一直未说出口的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.19,0:23:36.28,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这坦诚相对的世界里 向我微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:45.46,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你的声音 让我的眼泪也变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.49,0:23:49.21,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是划过我生命唯一的流星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.78,0:00:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 我说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.70,0:00:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱们坐同桌还是头一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.77,0:00:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离诹访君也很近
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 跟他离得有点儿远了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特君 会不会喜欢吃卷心菜肉卷呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.45,0:00:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦 有意味深长的电波正在飞来飞去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.80,0:00:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没飞来飞去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 认真了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相会是怎样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说不是这样啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.33,0:00:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.95,0:00:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑠璃你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.22,0:00:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 别生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.95,0:00:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是透过玻璃窗也无所谓的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}这个……是术语么？透过玻璃窗也可以接吻的人么……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.12,0:01:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是完全不认识的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全……不认识什么的……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.71,0:01:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这是不好的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 真是死板啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚上任的班长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.29,0:01:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是挺好吗 还隔着玻璃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.18,0:01:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是特纳西·塔科特君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.73,0:01:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是渡边加奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴能坐在你附近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是透过玻璃窗也无所谓的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 可能不是吧……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.65,0:01:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我还是要先申明一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.16,0:01:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说结婚……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.06,0:01:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是……是那个「结婚」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 人妻高中女生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.02,0:02:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请叫我Mrs渡边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰一下可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后 有时间吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 稍微陪我一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.45,0:02:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是love love呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.39,0:02:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新藤诹访
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是不是也是透过玻璃窗也无所谓的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车轮啊 车轮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大的车轮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我仿佛正在被本该由我驾驭的巨大的车轮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碾碎……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是三年级的远藤纱理奈部长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是特纳西·塔科特君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临戏剧部「夜间飞行」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两位你已经认识了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年级的山姿夏加学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及与我们同一年级的姿芽泰加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别叫我「学姐」 少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是 在学校里不要叫「少爷」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痒啊 别这样副部长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副部长……是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的美少年气场散发出来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很适合登上舞台呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你启动了Cybody
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是标志？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这个是什么留下的伤痕吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}津津有味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤痕和标志重叠在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没听说过这种事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有很多想问的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:06:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 他昨晚是为了保护和子而战的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是白马王子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经可以了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那帮家伙绑架她的理由是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那帮家伙到底是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天 你启动Cybody的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围的世界变成什么样了 你还记得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入奇怪的空间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 只有在那个奇怪的空间Cybody才能行动自如
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果启动cybody 世界的时间就会停止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在cybody只有在那个zero空间才能够活动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在普通的时空中不过是个巨大的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果能在普通的时空中活动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从军事政治经济各方面世界都会发生变化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而以此为目的的家伙现在正在这个岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戏剧部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(619,224)}绮罗星十字团的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团第二队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.44,0:07:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Banishing Age」代表人 首领
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团第三队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Bougainvilleae」代表人 Everonu
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团第四队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「成人银行」代表人 头取
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:08:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团第五队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Filament」代表人 Scarlet Kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团第六队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「科学工会」代表人 格林教授（Professor Green）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 绮罗星十字团总会开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.11,0:08:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我们解开了气多之巫女的封印进入了第二阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们终于用电气柩使cybody活动了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 各位 我们快乐日子也伴随着新试炼的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是真的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在现实中坐上了cybody
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是第三阶段？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而其那个没见过的cybody道伯恩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摧毁了我们伙伴的cybody
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 「Filament」的擅自行动也是个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开南方女巫的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来打算以后行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为有成员暴走表示抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装腔作势
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scarlet Kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应由「Filament」自身承担责任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁该负责？虽然现在首领拥有指挥权
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他不是支配着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.56,0:09:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不管怎样领导总是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 今晚的提案……怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说敌对的cybody是不可原谅的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那个让人不快的道伯恩击破的人当然就是领导
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在踏上旅途之前都保有指挥权
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无异议
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无异议
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无异议
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无异议
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赋予我们荣光 然后带给银河美少年毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的事和应该做的事合二为一的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能听见世界的声音么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是 对人生的……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿舍长！现在是男生的入浴时间啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从哪里进来的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密入口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.48,0:10:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我们来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.98,0:10:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在一年级学生中很流行的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔着玻璃接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有玻璃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔着不存在的玻璃接吻不就是个普通的吻吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿舍……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又穿着泳衣做100回单杠翻转上杠么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来看银河美少年的屁股的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔治怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}上一集给出的资料为本田逢司 以后将会按照官网更名为本田乔治
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alephisto被破坏了连StarDriver的资格都被剥夺了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也无可奈何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙意外的韧性很强所以……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能就这么结束？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会去复仇吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的话一定能成功 但是急不来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让希望之星闪耀是我们「Filament」吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长你不认为塔科特可能是他们的间谍吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不认为哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你能断言他不是呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特不是这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.77,0:12:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为和副部长关系很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在说认真的话题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很认真的在说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于那些家伙开始直接瞄准和子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明拥有能够操作最强Cybody并能使用Apprivoiser的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却不使用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为我在阻止着他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的和其他的人不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被如此重视着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们二位的婚约关系 他已经知道了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概从别人那里听说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.68,0:13:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好舒服的风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南十字学园吗 太有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,yes yes yes yes 太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}荡漾了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scarlet Kiss的第一个阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是操纵亲吻过的男人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那家伙确实真的爱慕着新藤诹访呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻人通常都不擅长等待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定很快就会行动的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜也睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鱼 和我说说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长 姜汁汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在的心情到底是怎样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我可能是为了和那些家伙战斗才来到了这个岛的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事请不要这么随便地说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣啊 那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也应该早就预料到在外面也有Star Driver了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是和那些家伙没有任何关系的有着正义感的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这和今后将持续下去的战斗完全不是一码事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是尽快转学的好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是 若绮罗星的人马教起真格来他是战胜不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了吗 稍微点些什么吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.39,0:14:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年坠入了爱河
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和在海滨相遇的女子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年陷入了热恋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:15:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 是爱情故事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地方在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是属于鱼的行星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣哦 小鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年是一个手法很娴熟的渔民
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.17,0:15:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字的话Sam怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sam 很好的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年Sam梦见自己以及与他邂逅的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐上小船 在光彩夺目的银河世界里畅游
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是Sam爱上的是那个少女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是那银河的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为人生的冒险仍在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开启吧 电力柩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apprivoiser
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们都干掉吧 Treteriauto！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飘舞的雪花是星之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着天体伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受到转瞬即逝的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今的一切都在黑白画之中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}悄然冻结的白色吐息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}想要传达的话语化为有形
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}肯定只有那份温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 快点座上来！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让我多等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}才能笼罩天空使它变得明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接嘴唇接触了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.74,0:17:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有隔玻璃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}被悲伤浸染的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}向着重叠的纯白色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把皆水之巫女的封印解开么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}我怀抱着无限温柔的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apprivoiser
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}在无人知晓的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}等待黎明的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}满载光辉踏上旅途的我有着无可预测的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}飘舞的雪花是星之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}向着天体伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}深信着转瞬即逝的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3}一切的未来都在黑白画之中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飒爽登场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道伯恩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太抢风头了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪打出头鸟 这句话你明白么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.31,0:18:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作真敏捷 是因为已经在第三阶段了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是把他毁掉有点可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙可不是个外行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不能容忍你们胡作非为了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会让你们对岛上的巫女们出手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过可不会像昨晚一样了哦 银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我的气势可是高达1亿伏特啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不讨厌纯真的男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦人的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.39,0:19:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来还有这一手 这可是个危机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉他 哲也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有我们filament 绮罗星才会如此闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.69,0:20:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点走吧 塔科特君 已经够了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算心怀恐惧 也要全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克服恐惧 勇往直前！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.68,0:20:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的终极一击！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Τ射线的光芒啊！将银河充斥吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:20:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}Τ读作Tau 为希腊字母
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪烁吧 Τ银河光线！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.56,0:21:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的出头鸟啊 就算你打他他也会出头的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.07,0:22:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的仇 我一定会替你报的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.32,0:22:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的肚子……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.05,0:22:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板麻烦来份卷心菜肉卷一份蛋包饭还有一份蛤肉羹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.34,0:22:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.46,0:23:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有钱是青春的特权！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.63,0:24:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没有生活费确实是个危机啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.31,0:24:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一人独居的女高中生的家里？！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.36,0:24:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 STAR DRIVER 闪亮的塔科特
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.27,0:24:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成人银行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.43,0:24:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的银河 一定闪烁着耀眼的光辉！
